description: Welcome to this spacious 2-bed, 2-bath condo in the heart of South Boston's City Point neighborhood. The open-concept layout seamlessly connects the chef’s kitchen to the living & dining areas, creating the perfect space for both everyday living and entertaining. The kitchen boasts sleek granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a convenient beverage fridge. Just off the kitchen, a cozy breakfast nook overlooks your private balcony and flows into the expansive living room featuring a shiplap fireplace. Down the hall, you’ll find the primary suite, complete with a walk-in closet and an en-suite bath. The second bedroom is sizable with a generous-sized closet. A deeded parking space is also included along with 2 designated visitor parking spaces & additional storage. The location is unbeatable, with easy access to the best of South Boston, from the nearby Pleasure Bay to local shops and vibrant restaurants. Open house 2/8 11:30-1pm & 2/9 12:30-2pm. Offers due 2/11 by noon.
